    <text>
        <body>
            <div frus:doc-dateTime-max="1919-12-24T13:00:00-05:00"
                frus:doc-dateTime-min="1919-12-24T13:00:00-05:00" n="839"
                subtype="historical-document" type="document" xml:id="d839">
                <note rend="inline" type="source">311.6124/6: Telegram</note>
                <head>
                    <hi rend="italic">The <gloss type="from">Secretary of State</gloss> to the
                        Commissioner at Riga</hi> (<persName type="to">
                        <hi rend="italic">Gade</hi>
                    </persName>)</head>
                <opener>
                    <dateline rendition="#right">
                        <placeName>
                            <hi rend="smallcaps">Washington</hi>
                        </placeName>, <date calendar="gregorian" when="1919-12-24T13:00:00-05:00">
                            <hi rend="italic">December 24, 1919—1 p.m.</hi>
                        </date>
                    </dateline>
                </opener>
                <p>Your 48 December 21, 1 a.m. United States transport <hi rend="italic">Buford</hi>
                    sailed from New York December 21st having on board 249 Russian subjects and will
                    reach Libau not later than January 12. You will be advised of ship’s
                    progress.</p>
                <p>F. W. Berkshire, Immigration Inspector in charge of party, carries letter of
                    introduction to you.</p>
                <p>Please perfect arrangements as far as possible before arrival of ship. You or a
                    responsible representative of yours should be at the port. Berkshire’s
                    instructions are simply to place himself in your hands and be guided by the
                    arrangements which you have made.</p>
                <p>Food of a value equivalent to cost of transporting Russians estimated at $4000
                    will be placed at disposal of Latvian authorities either being shipped by first
                    opportunity or found for them in Europe.</p>
                <closer>
                    <signed>
                        <hi rend="smallcaps">Lansing</hi>
                    </signed>
                </closer>
            </div>
        </body>
    </text>
